text.__SUMMARY__: Bulbophyllum biflorum (two-flowered bulbophyllum) is a species of orchid. This species was found in Java, Sumatra, Bali, Borneo, the Philippines and the Thai and Malaysian peninsula. The flower size is 7.5 cm long.
